    "summary": "The user expresses deep despair and hopelessness rooted in insurmountable financial debt, eventually hinting at suicidal ideation as a way to escape the pressure. The assistant responds with empathy, provides practical financial advice to address the root cause, and ultimately performs a standard safety pivot by providing crisis hotline information when the user explicitly mentions ending their life.",
